Package com.flightbookings.flight_bookings.models

Class Passenger

java.lang.Object
com.flightbookings.flight_bookings.models.Passenger
@Entity public class Passenger extends Object
Represents a passenger entity in the system. Contains details about the passenger's identity, contact information, and associated bookings.
